Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上溯至宇宙初始 周遭还只是一片漆黑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时 忽地一声巨响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then... Bang!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间空间以及物质皆由此发端{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此后不断膨胀 延伸 永无止境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一天 新的发现都在不断为我们解开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕴藏于这里的那些神秘莫测{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mysterious, the mind-blowing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人大开眼界 致命的秘密{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the deadly secrets of a place we call{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们称这个地方为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在一个陌生的星球举步维艰{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You're lost on an alien planet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}食物所剩无几{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Food is running low.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氧气补给日渐减少{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oxygen is running out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救助也在遥不可及的地点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Help is 100 million miles away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火星是一个致命的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Mars, it's a lethal place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里才能避免受宇宙辐射的伤害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Where can you hide from blasts of space radiation?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带电粒子会射向我们地表的宇航员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Charged particles would be hitting any astronauts that we had on the surface.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们没有防护措施{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They would not be protected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如何才能抵御致命的尘暴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}How can you stand up to a deadly dust storm?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火星上的尘土能侵蚀掉航天服{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The dust on Mars could eat away at the fabric of a space suit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是非常可怕的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That would be catastrophic.{\r}
