Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紧急降落火星后 你如何能够生还{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}How can you survive crash-landing on Mars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类迫降在火星上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Humans crash landing on Mars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在恶劣的环境中求生存{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Struggling to survive on a hostile world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一直是科幻电影热门的素材{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's been a favorite theme of science-fiction movies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这其中有许多事都搞错了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They got a lot of things wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是包括美国在内的许多国家的宇航局{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But NASA and other space agencies{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正筹备要在未来几十年内将人类送上火星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are planning to send people to the red planet in the next few decades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我们要考虑火星上迫降和生存的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So the questions of crash-landing and survival have to be taken seriously.{\r}
