Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是将探索队送上火星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You're sending a mission to Mars,{\r}
