Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步走错{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All it takes is one thing to go wrong...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整盘皆输{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Then you've lost the whole mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本节目是根据最近的科研成果{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This program, based on recent scientific information,{\r}
