Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象一下 国际探索队将去探索火星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Imagine that international crew has been selected to explore Mars{\r}
