Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电影的这一部分倒是说对了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, the movies got that part right.{\r}
