Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会把谁送上火星呢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Who would you send to Mars?{\r}
