Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你希望你的团队每个方面都有能手{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You want, uh, aces at many trades on your crew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队员最重要的能力就是维修能力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The most important skill among the crew is that of mechanic.{\r}
