Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是实地考察科学家 他们能够{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is that of field scientist, people that are qualified to{\r}
