Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要两个史考特和两个斯波克{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}two Scottys and two Spocks.{\r}
