Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与那些旧时的科幻电影中看到的不同{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Unlike the case in many old science-fiction movies,{\r}
