Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们将用此车进行一次长途旅行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}packed along with them on the hab.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一辆小型短程漫游车{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A smaller rover, for shorter trips,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经在着陆点就位{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}has been pre-positioned at the landing site{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旁边就是宇航员的返回舱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}along with the astronauts' ride home,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是返回地球舱 简称返地舱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the Earth Return Vehicle, or ERV.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它不仅在等待宇航员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ERV isn't just waiting for the astronauts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它还在将火星资源转化为火箭燃料和可用空气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's transforming martian resources into rocket fuel and breathable air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}返地舱有一个泵 能抽进火星的空气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Earth Return Vehicle runs a pump which sucks in the martian air,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里二氧化碳含量为95%{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which is 95% carbon dioxide gas,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们可以用这些二氧化碳{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and we can react that carbon dioxide gas{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我们从地球带来的少量氢气混合反应{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with a small amount of hydrogen that we've brought from Earth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}便能产生大量的甲烷 燃料和氧气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to produce a large supply of methane fuel and oxygen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的四名宇航员在返地舱附近登陆火星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Your crew of four astronauts land on Mars near the Earth return Vehicle,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们把生活舱当作实验室和考察基地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they use their habitat as their laboratory, as their exploration base,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考察结束后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but when they're done,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们就坐返地舱返回地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they get in the Earth Return Vehicle and they fly back to Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们将生活舱留在火星上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They leave the hab behind on Mars,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次探索我们都会为基地增加一个生活舱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so each time we do this we add another hab to the base,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and before you know it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们就能在火星开始建立人类定居地了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we've got the beginning of the first human settlement on a new world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们应该在火星哪里着陆呢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So where should we land on Mars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火星很令人着迷 那里有许多有趣的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, Mars is a fascinating planet... There's a lot of interesting areas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}选择赤道附近的地点也许会好一些{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It might be better, initially, to choose a region near the equator,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最好是平坦区域 但要靠近地貌奇特的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}especially a flat area, but also near geologically interesting features.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生活舱降落的技术必须万无一失{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One thing that mustn't go wrong is the hab's landing technique,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即大气煞车法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}called aerobraking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大气煞车法是利用火星大气层的摩擦力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Aerobraking is the art of using the friction of the martian atmosphere{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}降低宇宙飞船的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to slow down the spacecraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}设想这就是进入火星大气层的生活舱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Imagine this ball is the habitat module entering the martian atmosphere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这根杆子就是火星 非常细小{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The pole is Mars, a very skinny Mars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在我可以用火箭慢慢降低它的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, I could use rockets to gently slow this thing down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在预设的地方着陆 也就是胶带的位置{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and land at the desired spot, where this duct tape is,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这就需要许多能量 也就是燃料{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but that would require a lot of energy, which requires fuel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃料很重且成本高{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that's heavy and expensive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}取而代之 我们可以用火星的大气层来减速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Instead, we could let the martian atmosphere slow the hab down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看呐 它正在慢慢减速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}See that, it's gently slowing down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而只有在最后 非常接近地表的时候{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And only near the very end, when it's getting very close to the surface,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们才需要用到减速火箭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}would we turn on some retrorockets{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有气球降落伞 即气伞{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and use a balloon parachute called a ballute{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使之在特定位置降落 比如胶带那里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to bring it to the desired location. Like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}风险就在于 如果进入的角度不对{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, the danger is that if the angle of entry is wrong{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是速度太快 那么就会导致{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or the speed is too fast, then, in fact,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摩擦超过防热罩的承受能力 减速伞和{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}friction can overwhelm the heat shield, the aeroshell,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}舱体会像流星一样在大气层中燃烧起来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the hab can burn up like a meteor in the martian atmosphere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要是微小的计算错误{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And even a slight miscalculation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都能导致硬着陆或是在错误地点着陆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}can lead to a landing that's too rough or in the wrong place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}着陆过程极其复杂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There's about a thousand things that have to happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利用防热罩进入大气层 速度会很快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Come in on a heat shield, going quite fast,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利用大气的摩擦来减速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}use the friction of the atmosphere to help slow you down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要把防热罩抛掉才能着陆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The heat shield, the heat shield needs to be jettisoned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在穿越大气层时要尽全力制动减速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You need to aerobrake through the atmosphere as much as you can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通过弹出降落伞来减缓下降速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You need to pop out a parachute to slow yourself down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近地面时很可能用到反推火箭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You probably then need retrorockets at the bottom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}落地后要把降落伞割断并丢弃{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You need to cut the parachute to get it away from you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在所有困难的步骤中 这步是难上加难{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is extremely difficult, among the most difficult things there is to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但在距离火星表面仅几公里处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Then, a few miles above the surface,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出现了非常困难的状况{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}something goes very wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生活舱猛地闯入巨大的火星尘暴中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The hab hurtles into a martian dust devil of terrifying proportions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火星尘暴其实是大气层中的气旋{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Dust devils on Mars are vortices in the atmosphere{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高速运转的气旋 卷起火星表面的沙尘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so rapidly spinning columns of air that lift dust off of the surface.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后吹散到大气中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And loft them into the atmosphere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目前地球上的尘暴高仅一两百米{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, on Earth, dust devils may only be a few hundred feet high,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但在火星上则高达5至6.5千米{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but on Mars, they can be 3 to 4 miles high.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尘暴的规模相当大{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So they're simply immense structures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尘暴吞噬了生活舱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The dust devil engulfs the hab.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将其抛离既定轨道 非常危险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Throwing it dangerously off course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从德州到哈萨克斯坦的跟踪台{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Tracking stations from Texas to Kazakhstan{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都密切关注着本次着陆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are following the descent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但因为火星实在太远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But Mars is so far away,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生活舱信号传输到地球要花费18分钟{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it takes 18 minutes for the hab's transmissions to reach Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收到生活舱将要迫降的消息时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When the signal comes through that the hab is headed for a crash-landing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇航员们早已迫降着陆了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the astronauts have already crashed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是着陆地点在哪 它们是否生还{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But where? And are they alive or dead?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起飞和着陆两个过程中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There's only one thing you can do at launch, and there's{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们唯一能做的 只有祈祷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}only one thing you can do at landing, and that's pray.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在火星的某处 宇航员们还活着{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Somewhere on Mars the astronauts are alive{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但联络中断{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but communications are out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们无法和地球进行联系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They can't talk to Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更糟的是尘暴使他们远离既定路线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Worse, the dust devil has taken them far off course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类首次登陆火星 真真正正是一次壮举{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When humans first land on Mars, it'll be a truly magnificent event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是史无前例的壮举{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One of the most historic events ever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我们的宇航员是紧急迫降的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But, you know, our astronauts crash-landed.{\r}
